column2: ENGLISH
The time for a common assembly has come
column4: Die Landsgemeinde steht vor der Tür.

column2: Call all the commoners together.
Now is a really bad time.
The Vassals will gather in the capital to cast votes about the current [This.GetTitle]
column4: Die Vasallen versammeln sich, um den [This.GetTitle] zu wählen.

column2: Your vassals will be angry for you breaking common law.
column4: Eure Vasallen werden ausser sich sein, weil ihr gemeines Recht brecht.

column2: Number of Electors
cast votes
votes
The [From.GetTitle] has called for a Common Assembly to be held in [From.Capital.GetName]. You can cast a vote about the election of the [From.GetTitle]. How do you want to vote.
column4: Der [From.GetTitle] hat die Landsgemeinde in  [From.Capital.GetName] einberufen. Ihr könnt eure Stimme über die Wahl des [From.GetTitle] abgeben.

column2: [From.GetFullName] did a good job. I support [From.GetHerHim] for reelection.
column4: [From.GetFullName] hat gute Arbeit geleistet. Ich unterstütze [From.GetHerHim] für die Wiederwahl.

column2: I want a change of leadership in the [GetFullBaseName]
A new  [From.GetTitle] will be elected from the election pool.
column4: Es wird ein neuer [From.GetTitle] aus dem Kollegium der Landsgemeinde gewählt.

column2: You support your current ruler.
I support our [This.GetTitle] and vote for [This.GetHersHis] reelection.
column4: Ich unterstütze unseren [This.GetTitle] und Stimme für [This.GetHersHis] Wiederwahl.

column2: I‘m very greatful for your trust.
I will not support [This.GetFullName] for another term.
column4: Ich werde [This.GetFullName] nicht für eine weitere Amtszeit wählen.

column2: So be it.
With [This.currentsupport.GetValue] [This.currentsupport.GetName] [This.GetFullName] is reelected.
I thank the Common Assembly for its support.
column4: Ich danke der Landsgemeinde für ihr vertrauen.

column2: With only [This.currentsupport.GetValue] [This.currentsupport.GetName] of [This.totalelectors.GetValue] [This.GetFullName] is not reelected.
column4: Mit nur [This.currentsupport.GetValue] [This.currentsupport.GetName] von [This.totalelectors.GetValue] Wurde [This.GetFullName] nicht wiedergewählt.

column2: Well that‘s how things go.
[From.GetFullName] was reelected as [From.GetTitle] with [From.currentsupport.GetValue] of  [This.totalelectors.GetValue] [This.currentsupport.GetName]
column4: [From.GetFullName] wurde mit [From.currentsupport.GetValue] von [From.totalelectors.GetValue] [From.currentsupport.GetName] wieder zum [From.GetTitle] gewählt.

column2: So nothing changes.
[From.GetFullName] was not reelected as [From.GetTitle] with [From.currentsupport.GetValue] of [From.totalelectors.GetValue] [This.currentsupport.GetName]
Intresting.
The time for a common assembly is approaching. In the next spring the law demands one to be held.
column4: Der Zeitpunkt für eine neue Landsgemeinde kommt näher. Im nächsten Frühling verlangt das Gesetz, dass die Stände zusammen treten.

column2: I should make preperations.
column4: Ich sollte die Vorbereitungen dafür treffen.
